41, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"the obstacles\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"focused eyes\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"her mount's steps\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Slaoui-Fellous Equestrian stables in Oakley in Southern England, Moroccan rider Nour Slaoui and her trusted steed, Cash in Hand, train almost daily.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\", \"score\": 0.999999999494321, \"rank\": 5.054820511166552e-10, \"text\": \"Oakley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\"}, {\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"score\": 0.999999906718135, \"rank\": 8.976764503665457e-08, \"text\": \"Moroccan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\"}, {\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Nour_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999999999699867, \"rank\": 2.9961232515061405e-11, \"text\": \"Nour\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Nour_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Nour_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Slaoui-Fellous Equestrian stables\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"Southern England\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"her trusted steed\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"Cash\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"Hand\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The deep bond between the duo will be put to the test as they head for the Paris Olympics in late July.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The deep bond\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"the duo\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"late July\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In early March, Slaoui secured qualification for the Olympics, making her the first rider from Morocco and the Arab world to compete in equestrian eventing.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 793, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"score\": 0.9999999793708414, \"rank\": 2.062716591138422e-08, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\"}, {\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_world\", \"score\": 0.9999980837374267, \"rank\": 1.247142902531638e-06, \"text\": \"Arab\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_world\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_world\"}, {\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999190281448, \"rank\": 8.097170082334589e-08, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"early March\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old credits her Olympic achievement to the special relationship she shares with her horse, the Cashman, as she endearingly calls him.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 29-year-old credits\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic achievement\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"the special relationship\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"her horse\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"the Cashman\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two began their Olympic journey five years ago and worked their way up through several competitions.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their Olympic journey\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"several competitions\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know each other by heart, and I am delighted to share this adventure with him,\\\" Slaoui told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999999873939488, \"rank\": 1.2580023364413279e-08, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heart\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"this adventure\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"Slaoui\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Slaoui - born in Casablanca, Morocco, in 1995 - had a natural knack for riding early on in her life, often accompanying her family on days-long treks across the Atlas Mountains on muleback.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casablanca\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.204432095867306e-18, \"text\": \"Casablanca\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casablanca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casablanca\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"score\": 0.9999999793708414, \"rank\": 2.062716591138422e-08, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a natural knack\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"days-long treks\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"the Atlas Mountains\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"muleback\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the age of 18, she took a gap year from her studies at Warwick University in England to train as a riding instructor at the National Riding School in Saumur, France.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Warwick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Warwick University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Warwick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Warwick\"}, {\"begin\": 1488, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.967067916424247, \"rank\": 0.027760383564178658, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1569, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.993556620960973, \"rank\": 0.006156856922730832, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"a gap year\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"her studies\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"a riding instructor\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Riding School\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"Saumur\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon returning to the UK, she continued her training alongside her coach, Deborah Fellous, and co-founded her stables in Oakley, where they now have 17 horses.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999915758053, \"rank\": 7.651501685644783e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deborah\", \"score\": 0.9999966665755972, \"rank\": 3.3334354839876084e-06, \"text\": \"Deborah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deborah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deborah\"}, {\"begin\": 1698, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\", \"score\": 0.999999999494321, \"rank\": 5.054820511166552e-10, \"text\": \"Oakley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oakley_Observatory\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her training\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"her stables\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"17 horses\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, her talent grew into a passion that led her to specialize in eventing.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"her talent\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"a passion\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The classification is equestrian's version of the triathlon, a gruelling three-day test of the partnership between horse and rider spread across three disciplines: dressage, cross-country and show jumping.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1847, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999190281448, \"rank\": 8.097170082334589e-08, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The classification\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"the triathlon\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"a gruelling three-day test\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"the partnership\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"horse\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1945}, {\"ngram\": \"rider\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"three disciplines\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At first, it required a lot of hard work and determination as I was keen on mastering not just a single discipline but the sport as a whole,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"not just a single discipline\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But, although it has been a steep learning curve, I knew in my gut, straight away, that I wanted to be a professional eventing rider.\\\"\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a steep learning curve\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"my gut\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional eventing rider\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Transitioning from riding as a hobby to pursuing it professionally was a significant shift for Slaoui, who struggled at first with figuring out how to go about it.\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hobby\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant shift\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"Slaoui\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a rider from the MENA (Middle East and North Africa) region, growing up, I had no exposure to eventing,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2530, \"end\": 2542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999941028364, \"rank\": 5.692432516007562e-09, \"text\": \"North Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rider\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"no exposure\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I only discovered the discipline when I moved to the United Kingdom for my studies, and so unlike most other competitors who have been competing from a young age, I had a lot to catch up on in a very short period.\\\"\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2660, \"end\": 2674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.99999998774274, \"rank\": 5.871635034308359e-09, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the discipline\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"my studies\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"most other competitors\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2727}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"a very short period\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After meeting Fellous, Slaoui had enough guidance to launch her international riding career.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Slaoui\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"enough guidance\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2872}, {\"ngram\": \"her international riding career\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What makes Nour a good competitor is that she is persevering,\\\" Fellous told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2929, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Nour_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999999999699867, \"rank\": 2.9961232515061405e-11, \"text\": \"Nour\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Nour_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Nour_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 2994, \"end\": 3004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999999873939488, \"rank\": 1.2580023364413279e-08, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She shows complete commitment to the sport and does not let bad performances affect her.\\\"\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"complete commitment\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"bad performances\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Slaoui was relatively inexperienced in eventing at first, having started only a couple of years prior, and she was searching for a young horse to progress with.\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Slaoui\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"a young horse\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then one day, she met Cash in Hand.\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cash\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"Hand\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I crossed paths with Cash in Hand about five years ago,\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"paths\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3312}, {\"ngram\": \"Cash\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"Hand\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What drew me to him was his wonderful temperament - a very genuine horse that always wanted to please from the get-go.\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his wonderful temperament\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"a very genuine horse\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"the get-go\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We trust and know each other inside out, which is crucial in all phases, especially in cross-country, where we tackle big, solid fences.\\\"\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all phases\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3561}, {\"ngram\": \"cross\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3582}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3590}, {\"ngram\": \"big, solid fences\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Khadija El Mrabti, a Moroccan equestrian rider and trainer based in the United Arab Emirates (UAE), eventing demands a high level of harmony and synchronisation between riders and their horses to navigate through its three stages.\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3642, \"end\": 3649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khadija_bint_